main

public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
Description copied from class: Maud
Call the swingInitialization() and start the mainFrame. By default Maud will run interactively starting the interface; if the -t argument is used Maud will run in text only and will process a default "textonly.ins" file where there should be the instructions on what and how to run the analysis. The textonly.ins file is in CIF format and must contain the analysis/es to run and the iterations number.
